1
00:01:30,800 --> 00:01:34,520
=Lady Liberty=

2
00:01:35,020 --> 00:01:37,940
=Episode 7=

3
00:01:40,700 --> 00:01:41,680
He got here this morning.

4
00:01:41,820 --> 00:01:43,060
No way he just got here.

5
00:01:43,540 --> 00:01:44,940
He still has his wine out.

6
00:01:45,140 --> 00:01:45,900
You have to

7
00:01:45,980 --> 00:01:47,100
hand it to our boss.

8
00:01:47,980 --> 00:01:49,180
Then, where is Ms. Lin?

9
00:01:49,800 --> 00:01:50,700
- Ms. Lin.
- Ms. Lin.

10
00:01:50,711 --> 00:01:51,644
- Ms. Lin.
- Ms. Lin.

11
00:01:52,740 --> 00:01:53,610
Look at him.

12
00:01:53,610 --> 00:01:54,933
- See that?
- Time for work.

13
00:01:55,000 --> 00:01:55,620
Morning, Ms. Lin.

14
00:01:55,620 --> 00:01:56,790
- Ms. Lin.
- Morning, Ms. Lin.

15
00:01:57,060 --> 00:01:58,320
- Back to work.
- Back to work.

16
00:02:13,222 --> 00:02:14,488
Why are you sleeping here?

17
00:02:14,940 --> 00:02:16,100
Why can't I sleep here?

18
00:02:16,500 --> 00:02:17,980
I bought this sofa, you know.

19
00:02:21,300 --> 00:02:21,980
What's up?

20
00:02:22,300 --> 00:02:23,500
Did you sleep? Did you go home?

21
00:02:23,740 --> 00:02:24,780
Go home and get some rest.

22
00:02:25,100 --> 00:02:26,380
She talked with me all night.

23
00:02:27,933 --> 00:02:29,590
I was working late,
and He Han came up...

24
00:02:29,600 --> 00:02:30,511
No need to explain.

25
00:02:30,940 --> 00:02:32,355
Just go. I need to get to work.

26
00:02:34,980 --> 00:02:36,244
I can't leave, Lin Zhanqiao.

27
00:02:36,340 --> 00:02:37,022
Listen to me.

28
00:02:37,180 --> 00:02:38,020
Do me a favor.

29
00:02:38,420 --> 00:02:38,860
What is it?

30
00:02:40,580 --> 00:02:41,980
Mimi has me cornered at my hotel.

31
00:02:42,420 --> 00:02:43,500
Come back with me.

32
00:02:43,740 --> 00:02:44,860
If she sees us together,

33
00:02:44,860 --> 00:02:45,620
she'll finally

34
00:02:45,620 --> 00:02:46,580
leave me alone.

35
00:02:46,860 --> 00:02:47,980
You created this mess,

36
00:02:47,980 --> 00:02:49,020
so clean it up yourself.

37
00:02:49,500 --> 00:02:50,020
I'm busy.

38
00:02:51,044 --> 00:02:52,660
So you'll leave me hanging,
Lin Zhanqiao?

39
00:02:53,260 --> 00:02:53,980
I was never loyal.

40
00:02:57,940 --> 00:02:59,533
Zhangzhu,
how about you come with me?

41
00:03:06,900 --> 00:03:07,580
Not a chance.

42
00:03:08,300 --> 00:03:09,100
Go home and rest up.

43
00:03:09,100 --> 00:03:10,470
Take the morning off.
Get some sleep.

44
00:03:10,488 --> 00:03:11,222
Thanks, Ms. Lin.

45
00:03:11,620 --> 00:03:11,980
Coffee.

46
00:03:12,100 --> 00:03:12,500
No thanks.

47
00:03:17,340 --> 00:03:17,740
What?

48
00:03:18,460 --> 00:03:19,333
Need a private chat?

49
00:03:21,580 --> 00:03:22,940
Do you remember the lore book

50
00:03:23,155 --> 00:03:24,533
for "Drunk Old Friend"?

51
00:03:25,500 --> 00:03:25,980
Of course.

52
00:03:26,180 --> 00:03:26,955
I threw it away.

53
00:03:27,980 --> 00:03:29,100
If you still have it,

54
00:03:29,620 --> 00:03:30,300
give it back.

55
00:03:31,688 --> 00:03:32,844
Have you forgotten?

56
00:03:33,180 --> 00:03:34,940
Someone plagiarized the Guazhou section,

57
00:03:34,940 --> 00:03:36,222
which is why we threw it away.

58
00:03:36,340 --> 00:03:36,740
Why?

59
00:03:37,177 --> 00:03:38,180
Is Gu Yan writing it now?

60
00:03:39,020 --> 00:03:40,420
He can't go through Guazhou.

61
00:03:40,420 --> 00:03:41,620
Take Zhichi Gorge instead.

62
00:03:41,700 --> 00:03:42,900
That's none of your business.

63
00:03:43,740 --> 00:03:45,420
The copyright for all project materials

64
00:03:45,540 --> 00:03:46,500
belongs to Chenxing.

65
00:03:47,020 --> 00:03:47,900
If you still have it,

66
00:03:48,100 --> 00:03:49,100
you should return it.

67
00:03:49,844 --> 00:03:50,900
Of course, you could say

68
00:03:51,140 --> 00:03:51,820
you lost it.

69
00:03:52,340 --> 00:03:53,155
Then, forget it.

70
00:03:54,780 --> 00:03:56,020
Still insisting on Guazhou?

71
00:03:56,100 --> 00:03:57,260
Fine. Very ambitious.

72
00:03:59,740 --> 00:04:00,780
I'll go back and look.

73
00:04:00,911 --> 00:04:02,140
If I find it, it's yours.

74
00:04:02,220 --> 00:04:03,700
It's useless to me anyway.

75
00:04:09,000 --> 00:04:10,577
Your dad's birthday is coming up.

76
00:04:10,660 --> 00:04:12,400
How are you celebrating?
Is your mom going?

77
00:04:16,940 --> 00:04:18,100
You're resuming updates soon.

78
00:04:18,940 --> 00:04:19,740
Are you ready?

79
00:04:21,260 --> 00:04:21,940
What if you lose

80
00:04:22,140 --> 00:04:23,010
to Gu Yan

81
00:04:23,010 --> 00:04:24,540
or Hong Qigong

82
00:04:24,800 --> 00:04:25,911
on the charts?

83
00:04:26,900 --> 00:04:28,020
I'll contact your dad.

84
00:04:28,140 --> 00:04:28,800
See you then.

85
00:04:29,340 --> 00:04:30,820
Is the breakup with Mimi sorted?

86
00:04:31,260 --> 00:04:31,900
Don't be late.

87
00:04:45,780 --> 00:04:46,620
See? I didn't lie.

88
00:04:47,420 --> 00:04:48,420
This apartment

89
00:04:48,820 --> 00:04:50,540
is the best unit in the building.

90
00:04:51,340 --> 00:04:52,220
The natural light,

91
00:04:53,620 --> 00:04:55,540
the decor, and the appliances

92
00:04:55,540 --> 00:04:56,580
are all top-tier.

93
00:04:57,500 --> 00:04:59,580
Your rent offer is way too low.

94
00:05:00,220 --> 00:05:01,940
It's hard to rent places out now.

95
00:05:02,940 --> 00:05:03,780
If you use an agent,

96
00:05:04,540 --> 00:05:06,180
they'll charge you a fee.

97
00:05:08,580 --> 00:05:11,060
If you love this building so much,

98
00:05:11,140 --> 00:05:12,020
how about I show you

99
00:05:12,260 --> 00:05:14,220
the smaller unit next door?

100
00:05:14,980 --> 00:05:16,180
It's also for rent.

101
00:05:16,340 --> 00:05:17,380
It's a one-bedroom?

102
00:05:20,220 --> 00:05:20,660
Too small.

103
00:05:22,140 --> 00:05:23,100
You live alone.

104
00:05:23,100 --> 00:05:24,220
How much space do you need?

105
00:05:27,888 --> 00:05:28,860
Is there someone else?

106
00:05:31,420 --> 00:05:33,140
Then, I can't rent to you.

107
00:05:33,540 --> 00:05:34,980
Even though

108
00:05:34,980 --> 00:05:36,180
I'm over you,

109
00:05:36,660 --> 00:05:38,420
if another man

110
00:05:38,420 --> 00:05:39,700
stays in my apartment,

111
00:05:40,340 --> 00:05:41,020
well...

112
00:05:41,900 --> 00:05:43,260
I'm paying rent.

113
00:05:43,700 --> 00:05:45,140
You're paying too little.

114
00:05:47,044 --> 00:05:48,770
You taking advantage of me is one thing.

115
00:05:48,770 --> 00:05:50,100
But another man, too?

116
00:05:50,460 --> 00:05:51,260
No way.

117
00:05:53,580 --> 00:05:54,260
It's settled.

118
00:05:54,260 --> 00:05:55,180
15,000 yuan a month.

119
00:05:55,860 --> 00:05:56,540
I'll live alone.

120
00:05:58,620 --> 00:05:59,580
If there's someone else?

121
00:05:59,900 --> 00:06:01,020
10,000 yuan per person.

122
00:06:04,980 --> 00:06:05,420
Deal.

123
00:06:11,940 --> 00:06:12,340
Hello.

124
00:06:28,020 --> 00:06:28,540
Dai Shan.

125
00:06:41,420 --> 00:06:42,660
I told him early on.

126
00:06:42,860 --> 00:06:45,020
A harem plot
in this chapter is dangerous.

127
00:06:45,700 --> 00:06:46,460
He didn't listen.

128
00:06:47,020 --> 00:06:47,844
Look at him now.

129
00:06:48,300 --> 00:06:49,420
His stats are tanking,

130
00:06:49,420 --> 00:06:50,540
and fans are angry.

131
00:06:51,260 --> 00:06:52,420
He comes to drink every day.

132
00:06:52,500 --> 00:06:53,900
He calls me when he's drunk,

133
00:06:54,100 --> 00:06:55,180
and vents for three hours.

134
00:06:55,660 --> 00:06:56,620
Says he needs to talk.

135
00:06:59,540 --> 00:07:00,620
I'm not an editor anymore.

136
00:07:01,140 --> 00:07:03,460
I'm his personal relationship guru.

137
00:07:03,940 --> 00:07:04,900
I think it's nice.

138
00:07:04,900 --> 00:07:05,900
He talks to you.

139
00:07:07,220 --> 00:07:08,044
I need to take this.

140
00:07:09,300 --> 00:07:09,900
(Ladies,)

141
00:07:10,620 --> 00:07:12,220
(stubbornly chasing a jerk)

142
00:07:12,220 --> 00:07:14,300
(means you lack self-respect.)

143
00:07:16,460 --> 00:07:17,100
(Sometimes,)

144
00:07:17,100 --> 00:07:19,220
(we can't help but reach out.)

145
00:07:19,700 --> 00:07:21,100
(Because we still love him.)

146
00:07:21,100 --> 00:07:22,500
(Because we haven't woken up.)

147
00:07:23,660 --> 00:07:25,860
(But after all the begging,)

148
00:07:25,860 --> 00:07:27,100
(pleading, and crying,)

149
00:07:27,460 --> 00:07:28,620
(in the end...)

150
00:07:30,660 --> 00:07:32,180
(He already has someone new.)

151
00:07:34,460 --> 00:07:36,540
(And it's someone he met at work.)

152
00:07:37,740 --> 00:07:39,140
(They've been together a while.)

153
00:07:39,380 --> 00:07:41,100
(And they never really ended it.)

154
00:07:42,580 --> 00:07:44,020
(Who is this person?)

155
00:07:45,940 --> 00:07:47,500
(I'll reveal it in my novel.)

156
00:07:47,620 --> 00:07:49,060
Met through work,

157
00:07:49,340 --> 00:07:50,580
and already together?

158
00:07:51,180 --> 00:07:52,180
It has to be Ms. Lin.

159
00:07:52,620 --> 00:07:54,780
Did He Han
and Ms. Lin stay together?

160
00:07:55,377 --> 00:07:56,300
Didn't they break up?

161
00:07:56,860 --> 00:07:58,100
Maybe they got back together.

162
00:07:59,260 --> 00:08:00,900
They are soulmates.

163
00:08:01,000 --> 00:08:02,355
The kind that are intertwined.

164
00:08:02,377 --> 00:08:03,220
You wouldn't get it.

165
00:08:03,260 --> 00:08:04,700
Do you believe everything you hear?

166
00:08:05,020 --> 00:08:06,660
What soul sees us as partners?

167
00:08:07,620 --> 00:08:08,620
Are you the love expert?

168
00:08:09,180 --> 00:08:10,580
Tell your authors to intertwine

169
00:08:10,580 --> 00:08:12,180
their male and female leads, then.

170
00:08:12,540 --> 00:08:13,260
Stop letting them

171
00:08:13,260 --> 00:08:14,620
stare longingly from afar.

172
00:08:15,140 --> 00:08:16,380
No one will read that!

173
00:08:25,700 --> 00:08:26,650
In a rush?

174
00:08:26,650 --> 00:08:27,260
Are you...

175
00:08:27,540 --> 00:08:28,980
I'm turning the place upside down.

176
00:08:28,980 --> 00:08:30,020
I can't find it.

177
00:08:30,180 --> 00:08:31,420
I'm not talking about that.

178
00:08:32,460 --> 00:08:33,500
I told you,

179
00:08:33,500 --> 00:08:35,460
don't drag me into Mimi's mess.

180
00:08:35,740 --> 00:08:36,660
What does she want?

181
00:08:37,020 --> 00:08:37,700
True stories?

182
00:08:37,860 --> 00:08:38,500
Live updates?

183
00:08:38,500 --> 00:08:39,700
Old loves and new flames?

184
00:08:40,900 --> 00:08:41,420
Listen up!

185
00:08:41,420 --> 00:08:42,820
If she dares to write about me,

186
00:08:43,220 --> 00:08:44,140
or makes up lies

187
00:08:44,140 --> 00:08:45,500
about us reconciling,

188
00:08:45,660 --> 00:08:46,940
to get clicks and reads,

189
00:08:46,940 --> 00:08:47,890
I can sue her!

190
00:08:47,890 --> 00:08:48,820
And I'll sue you, too!

191
00:08:52,700 --> 00:08:54,060
I didn't provoke her.

192
00:08:54,220 --> 00:08:55,580
We already broke up.

193
00:08:55,660 --> 00:08:57,300
She always twists my words.

194
00:08:58,060 --> 00:08:58,900
Lin Zhanqiao, listen.

195
00:08:59,420 --> 00:09:00,666
The truth speaks for itself.

196
00:09:01,500 --> 00:09:02,780
Whatever she wants to say,

197
00:09:02,780 --> 00:09:03,820
just let her say it.

198
00:09:03,940 --> 00:09:05,850
If this stops you
from getting a new boyfriend,

199
00:09:05,850 --> 00:09:06,410
let me know.

200
00:09:06,410 --> 00:09:08,020
I'll talk to him for you.

201
00:09:08,020 --> 00:09:08,990
I'm done talking to you!

202
00:09:09,020 --> 00:09:10,000
It's making it worse!

203
00:09:15,620 --> 00:09:15,980
Zhangzhu.

204
00:09:24,340 --> 00:09:25,980
You gave her time off, so she went home.

205
00:09:27,260 --> 00:09:27,940
Do me a favor.

206
00:09:28,140 --> 00:09:29,060
Contact Dingqi.

207
00:09:29,660 --> 00:09:30,220
Tell them

208
00:09:30,500 --> 00:09:32,088
to make Mimi delete that smear video.

209
00:09:32,260 --> 00:09:33,088
Right, Ms. Lin.

210
00:09:36,260 --> 00:09:36,820
Good news.

211
00:09:36,888 --> 00:09:38,300
Ms. Wu from Zhiyuan Investment

212
00:09:38,300 --> 00:09:39,955
wants to see you this afternoon.

213
00:09:41,740 --> 00:09:42,290
Tell her

214
00:09:42,290 --> 00:09:43,288
I'll see her at 2 PM.

215
00:09:43,340 --> 00:09:43,700
Also,

216
00:09:43,900 --> 00:09:44,450
tell Gu Yan

217
00:09:44,450 --> 00:09:45,130
not to come today.

218
00:09:45,130 --> 00:09:45,500
Okay.

219
00:09:46,060 --> 00:09:46,460
Sir.

220
00:09:46,860 --> 00:09:47,540
You can't go in.

221
00:09:48,940 --> 00:09:49,660
Sir!

222
00:09:50,820 --> 00:09:51,660
Please wait a moment.

223
00:10:05,420 --> 00:10:05,930
Sir!

224
00:10:05,930 --> 00:10:06,780
You can't come in.

225
00:10:07,260 --> 00:10:07,620
Ms. Lin.

226
00:10:08,020 --> 00:10:09,555
Zhangzhu's father is here to see you.

227
00:10:12,260 --> 00:10:13,340
You're Zhangzhu's boss?

228
00:10:14,540 --> 00:10:15,180
Lin Zhanqiao,

229
00:10:15,540 --> 00:10:16,460
head of Chenxing.

230
00:10:20,300 --> 00:10:21,220
You owe me an apology.

231
00:10:21,500 --> 00:10:21,940
Who is he?

232
00:10:22,460 --> 00:10:22,980
I don't know.

233
00:10:23,220 --> 00:10:23,980
I think it's

234
00:10:24,620 --> 00:10:25,340
Zhangzhu's dad.

235
00:10:27,180 --> 00:10:27,700
For what?

236
00:10:30,260 --> 00:10:30,900
How old are you?

237
00:10:36,220 --> 00:10:37,420
You're clearly not a child.

238
00:10:40,180 --> 00:10:41,660
My daughter is only twenty-two.

239
00:10:42,620 --> 00:10:45,380
You need to apologize
for filling her head

240
00:10:45,460 --> 00:10:46,260
with terrible ideas.

241
00:10:49,020 --> 00:10:50,770
What terrible ideas did I teach her?

242
00:10:50,770 --> 00:10:52,733
Encouraging her
not to call my new wife Mom.

243
00:10:54,260 --> 00:10:55,860
That she has the right to accept

244
00:10:56,340 --> 00:10:57,170
this new mother,

245
00:10:57,170 --> 00:10:58,500
and the right to reject her.

246
00:10:59,700 --> 00:11:00,380
"Our home

247
00:11:00,688 --> 00:11:01,844
is her father's home."

248
00:11:01,860 --> 00:11:02,740
"It isn't her home."

249
00:11:03,540 --> 00:11:04,333
"Live elsewhere"

250
00:11:04,500 --> 00:11:05,420
"under another's roof."

251
00:11:06,380 --> 00:11:08,540
"She deserves
a real home of her own."

252
00:11:10,020 --> 00:11:11,660
What kind of boss are you?

253
00:11:12,220 --> 00:11:14,220
Aren't you overstepping?

254
00:11:15,380 --> 00:11:16,570
She comes here to work,

255
00:11:16,570 --> 00:11:17,860
not to be brainwashed.

256
00:11:18,660 --> 00:11:20,100
You seem educated.

257
00:11:20,660 --> 00:11:21,940
You should know better than me,

258
00:11:22,260 --> 00:11:23,500
that the most important quality

259
00:11:23,860 --> 00:11:25,020
is filial piety.

260
00:11:25,380 --> 00:11:25,740
Right?

261
00:11:28,380 --> 00:11:28,900
First of all,

262
00:11:29,700 --> 00:11:31,140
I never said that to Zhangzhu.

263
00:11:31,140 --> 00:11:32,540
If not you, then who?

264
00:11:32,740 --> 00:11:33,820
Are there other bosses?

265
00:11:34,860 --> 00:11:35,820
It's this place.

266
00:11:36,180 --> 00:11:37,250
You're ruining my daughter.

267
00:11:37,250 --> 00:11:37,660
Second,

268
00:11:38,466 --> 00:11:39,620
I had never met you before.

269
00:11:40,860 --> 00:11:42,050
And I just found out

270
00:11:42,050 --> 00:11:42,980
your new wife would be

271
00:11:43,100 --> 00:11:44,220
Zhangzhu's new mother.

272
00:11:44,900 --> 00:11:46,140
I would've said the same

273
00:11:46,220 --> 00:11:46,980
had she asked me.

274
00:11:47,340 --> 00:11:49,220
I don't see anything wrong with it.

275
00:11:50,300 --> 00:11:51,540
Zhangzhu is twenty-two.

276
00:11:51,540 --> 00:11:52,580
She's not twelve.

277
00:11:53,180 --> 00:11:54,100
She is your daughter.

278
00:11:54,300 --> 00:11:55,140
But she is also

279
00:11:55,140 --> 00:11:56,860
an independent adult.

280
00:11:57,222 --> 00:11:58,420
She deserves your respect.

281
00:11:59,820 --> 00:12:00,580
Let me tell you.

282
00:12:01,540 --> 00:12:02,780
I do not allow my daughter

283
00:12:02,780 --> 00:12:03,860
to keep working here.

284
00:12:05,020 --> 00:12:06,140
Then please ask

285
00:12:06,140 --> 00:12:07,219
your daughter's opinion.

286
00:12:07,220 --> 00:12:08,580
And respect her decision.

287
00:12:11,660 --> 00:12:12,780
I can't talk to you.

288
00:12:13,540 --> 00:12:14,060
Ms. Liu.

289
00:12:14,140 --> 00:12:14,740
It's Ms. Lin.

290
00:12:26,460 --> 00:12:27,180
Let's go.

291
00:12:42,380 --> 00:12:42,900
What?

292
00:12:43,420 --> 00:12:45,020
Was calling not personal enough?

293
00:12:45,100 --> 00:12:46,220
You had to come in person?

294
00:12:46,380 --> 00:12:46,980
Let me ask you.

295
00:12:48,260 --> 00:12:49,340
What did you tell Zhangzhu?

296
00:12:50,300 --> 00:12:51,220
Her dad just came here

297
00:12:51,220 --> 00:12:52,660
and chewed me out!

298
00:12:52,980 --> 00:12:54,940
He went to your office
and chewed you out?

299
00:12:55,100 --> 00:12:56,660
Doesn't that prove I was right?

300
00:12:56,660 --> 00:12:57,620
Her dad is the problem.

301
00:12:57,980 --> 00:12:59,260
Zhangzhu is my assistant.

302
00:12:59,700 --> 00:13:00,540
I finally found

303
00:13:00,540 --> 00:13:01,660
a competent assistant.

304
00:13:01,844 --> 00:13:03,100
Your late-night talk with her

305
00:13:03,100 --> 00:13:04,340
could've made her quit!

306
00:13:04,540 --> 00:13:05,933
Can you get me a new one, then?

307
00:13:07,020 --> 00:13:07,700
Before you speak,

308
00:13:07,700 --> 00:13:09,500
use your brain
and think of the consequences!

309
00:13:09,660 --> 00:13:10,020
Hold on.

310
00:13:10,460 --> 00:13:12,220
Who could've seen this coming?

311
00:13:12,540 --> 00:13:13,260
Right?

312
00:13:13,900 --> 00:13:15,020
You know what I said.

313
00:13:15,020 --> 00:13:16,290
So you must agree with me.

314
00:13:16,290 --> 00:13:17,700
You probably even admire me.

315
00:13:18,100 --> 00:13:19,340
You're pretending to be mad.

316
00:13:19,340 --> 00:13:20,140
I can tell.

317
00:13:20,540 --> 00:13:21,300
But I have to say,

318
00:13:21,660 --> 00:13:22,420
Zhangzhu is a

319
00:13:22,420 --> 00:13:23,820
smart girl who knows what's right.

320
00:13:24,140 --> 00:13:25,260
Is she back at the office?

321
00:13:25,780 --> 00:13:26,740
She's my assistant.

322
00:13:26,740 --> 00:13:27,660
If anything comes up,

323
00:13:27,660 --> 00:13:28,780
I can handle it.

324
00:13:28,940 --> 00:13:29,620
Why don't you

325
00:13:29,620 --> 00:13:30,900
go talk to her dad?

326
00:13:31,380 --> 00:13:32,420
Stop running your mouth

327
00:13:32,420 --> 00:13:33,820
and blaming me, okay?

328
00:13:33,911 --> 00:13:34,780
Yes, you're not busy.

329
00:13:34,780 --> 00:13:35,740
You can ride your bike.

330
00:13:35,740 --> 00:13:37,420
But I can't. I have to work!

331
00:13:37,500 --> 00:13:38,300
I'm working, too.

332
00:13:38,300 --> 00:13:39,500
I'm looking for the lore book.

333
00:13:39,740 --> 00:13:40,620
If you have time,

334
00:13:40,620 --> 00:13:41,940
we can sit down and review it.

335
00:13:41,940 --> 00:13:43,340
We can probably figure it out.

336
00:13:43,660 --> 00:13:44,260
I'm busy.

337
00:13:50,580 --> 00:13:51,700
It's expensive.

338
00:14:18,220 --> 00:14:18,980
Your boss is here.

339
00:14:19,620 --> 00:14:20,460
Sorry, Ms. Lin.

340
00:14:20,820 --> 00:14:21,740
Give me a second.

341
00:14:21,980 --> 00:14:22,420
It's fine.

342
00:14:22,700 --> 00:14:24,020
I'm heading back to the office.

343
00:14:24,340 --> 00:14:25,100
I'll contact you.

344
00:14:25,180 --> 00:14:26,660
Just give me five minutes!

345
00:14:27,100 --> 00:14:27,660
No rush.

346
00:14:27,940 --> 00:14:29,420
Finish today's work first.

347
00:14:29,780 --> 00:14:31,460
We can deal
with the Guazhou arc later.

348
00:14:31,780 --> 00:14:32,355
I'm leaving.

349
00:14:37,780 --> 00:14:38,300
What's wrong?

350
00:14:40,980 --> 00:14:42,860
Ms. Lin shouldn't see us like this.

351
00:14:44,500 --> 00:14:45,740
Isn't this normal?

352
00:14:55,660 --> 00:14:56,580
Mei, where are you?

353
00:15:05,700 --> 00:15:07,460
Didn't you know Gu Yan had a girlfriend?

354
00:15:08,380 --> 00:15:09,460
I knew.

355
00:15:09,860 --> 00:15:11,355
Then, why are you freaking out?

356
00:15:12,980 --> 00:15:14,580
I wasn't prepared for it.

357
00:15:15,740 --> 00:15:17,540
I used to visit He Han like this.

358
00:15:17,660 --> 00:15:19,020
And I never ran into

359
00:15:19,020 --> 00:15:20,300
such an awkward situation.

360
00:15:21,820 --> 00:15:23,380
He Han was your boyfriend.

361
00:15:23,700 --> 00:15:24,460
Gu Yan isn't.

362
00:15:24,644 --> 00:15:25,660
Back then, He Han and I

363
00:15:25,660 --> 00:15:26,900
weren't even dating.

364
00:15:27,340 --> 00:15:28,580
We just met,

365
00:15:28,580 --> 00:15:29,380
and worked together.

366
00:15:29,620 --> 00:15:31,420
Nothing like this ever happened.

367
00:15:32,220 --> 00:15:33,580
That's because he's experienced,

368
00:15:33,580 --> 00:15:35,020
and hid it from you.

369
00:15:35,940 --> 00:15:37,340
Mimi just dropped a bombshell.

370
00:15:37,700 --> 00:15:39,020
She said He Han is two-timing.

371
00:15:40,540 --> 00:15:41,500
When did this happen?

372
00:15:42,340 --> 00:15:43,340
"Wide Awake"

373
00:15:43,340 --> 00:15:44,260
updated this morning.

374
00:15:47,060 --> 00:15:49,220
(Wide Awake)

375
00:15:53,340 --> 00:15:54,400
Am I that kind of person?

376
00:15:54,660 --> 00:15:55,860
We already broke up.

377
00:15:56,180 --> 00:15:57,020
Why would I go back

378
00:15:57,220 --> 00:15:59,220
to fight a woman like Mimi over He Han?

379
00:16:00,500 --> 00:16:02,220
Even I wouldn't believe it if I said it.

380
00:16:09,780 --> 00:16:10,460
Another update.

381
00:16:11,140 --> 00:16:14,020
The Jerk's Romance
with His Older Manager.

382
00:16:20,300 --> 00:16:23,100
(Chapter 7: The Jerk's Romance
with His Older Manager)

383
00:16:23,100 --> 00:16:23,820
(Ladies,)

384
00:16:23,980 --> 00:16:27,020
(the worst part isn't being cheated on.)

385
00:16:27,580 --> 00:16:29,700
(It's realizing I was the other woman.)

386
00:16:31,100 --> 00:16:33,260
(He was with his manager all along.)

387
00:16:33,660 --> 00:16:34,740
(I was fooled for so long.)

388
00:16:34,740 --> 00:16:36,220
(How could I be so stupid?)

389
00:16:38,820 --> 00:16:41,260
(They are two of a kind.)

390
00:16:41,620 --> 00:16:44,460
I could hear you laughing
from the elevator.

391
00:16:44,460 --> 00:16:45,620
Is it that funny?

392
00:16:46,500 --> 00:16:47,940
How is this not funny?

393
00:16:49,020 --> 00:16:50,700
Lin Zhanqiao thought it was her.

394
00:16:50,980 --> 00:16:53,940
She even went to Dingqi,
demanding they delete the video.

395
00:16:54,180 --> 00:16:56,460
I can just imagine the look on her face.

396
00:16:56,460 --> 00:16:57,660
I never thought

397
00:16:58,820 --> 00:17:00,140
I'd fail so miserably

398
00:17:00,140 --> 00:17:01,580
in love.

399
00:17:01,940 --> 00:17:02,820
Oh my goodness.

400
00:17:02,820 --> 00:17:04,380
What is all this?

401
00:17:06,500 --> 00:17:07,220
Did you do this?

402
00:17:07,740 --> 00:17:09,260
Would she have left otherwise?

403
00:17:10,140 --> 00:17:12,500
You mean you're He Han's new flame?

404
00:17:12,940 --> 00:17:14,340
After he and Lin Zhanqiao broke up,

405
00:17:14,340 --> 00:17:15,420
we got together.

406
00:17:16,220 --> 00:17:17,260
I don't believe it.

407
00:17:17,980 --> 00:17:19,420
You look much older than him.

408
00:17:21,940 --> 00:17:22,820
Listen to me.

409
00:17:22,900 --> 00:17:25,660
This will really help

410
00:17:25,660 --> 00:17:27,340
with tonight's click rates.

411
00:17:27,820 --> 00:17:29,140
What were you going to write?

412
00:17:30,580 --> 00:17:31,620
That his new flame

413
00:17:31,620 --> 00:17:33,260
is another female author?

414
00:17:34,060 --> 00:17:35,980
They could sue you for slander.

415
00:17:38,020 --> 00:17:38,866
Lin Zhanqiao...

416
00:17:39,900 --> 00:17:40,620
Is it original

417
00:17:40,780 --> 00:17:42,140
to rekindle an old flame?

418
00:17:42,900 --> 00:17:43,500
No.

419
00:17:43,660 --> 00:17:45,460
Plus, what chapter

420
00:17:45,740 --> 00:17:46,460
are you even on?

421
00:17:46,900 --> 00:17:49,740
If they get back together now,

422
00:17:49,740 --> 00:17:51,460
what's left to write?

423
00:17:52,340 --> 00:17:53,170
That's why

424
00:17:53,170 --> 00:17:55,700
you have to use my idea.

425
00:17:55,820 --> 00:17:57,180
It perfectly satisfies

426
00:17:57,380 --> 00:17:59,980
their craving for gossip.

427
00:18:00,380 --> 00:18:00,940
Plus,

428
00:18:01,460 --> 00:18:02,740
the jerk persona

429
00:18:03,088 --> 00:18:04,333
is taken to the next level.

430
00:18:04,644 --> 00:18:05,210
I'm serious.

431
00:18:05,210 --> 00:18:06,900
This is pure genius.

432
00:18:07,060 --> 00:18:07,980
Never mind Mimi.

433
00:18:08,220 --> 00:18:09,780
Even I'm in awe.

434
00:18:10,260 --> 00:18:11,700
Come on. Sit down.

435
00:18:12,980 --> 00:18:14,130
Absolutely brilliant.

436
00:18:14,130 --> 00:18:15,060
A total masterpiece.

437
00:18:16,780 --> 00:18:17,780
She just wanted

438
00:18:17,780 --> 00:18:19,860
to milk you for content.

439
00:18:19,980 --> 00:18:21,580
So I taught her a lesson.

440
00:18:25,420 --> 00:18:26,780
I can never repay you.

441
00:18:27,020 --> 00:18:28,380
Except with my body.

442
00:18:28,660 --> 00:18:29,340
I may flirt

443
00:18:29,340 --> 00:18:30,940
with young girls.

444
00:18:31,180 --> 00:18:32,133
But it means nothing.

445
00:18:32,180 --> 00:18:33,500
I actually value brains.

446
00:18:33,577 --> 00:18:34,460
With a mind like yours,

447
00:18:34,580 --> 00:18:35,700
age is just a number.

448
00:18:41,860 --> 00:18:43,580
I'm not interested in younger men.

449
00:18:44,180 --> 00:18:45,540
I only want your drafts.

450
00:18:45,780 --> 00:18:47,660
Save your brains and everything else

451
00:18:48,060 --> 00:18:49,180
for the other girls.

452
00:18:53,340 --> 00:18:54,460
You really won't consider it?

453
00:18:58,460 --> 00:19:00,020
You like older men.

454
00:19:00,300 --> 00:19:01,420
How old is Mr. Fan?

455
00:19:01,540 --> 00:19:02,700
He's got to be eighty-five.

456
00:19:03,020 --> 00:19:04,100
Isn't that too old?

457
00:19:04,300 --> 00:19:06,620
Twenty-year-olds
probably think you're old, too.

458
00:19:07,260 --> 00:19:08,740
But you don't mind, do you?

459
00:19:08,940 --> 00:19:09,660
Fair point.

460
00:19:10,260 --> 00:19:11,740
I should hit the gym more.

461
00:19:15,260 --> 00:19:15,660
Catch.

462
00:19:18,500 --> 00:19:19,444
Take it for a spin.

463
00:19:20,620 --> 00:19:22,220
Thanks, boss.

464
00:19:22,220 --> 00:19:23,060
Don't mention it.

465
00:19:23,740 --> 00:19:24,980
Being generous to my girlfriend

466
00:19:25,060 --> 00:19:26,660
only makes me look good.

467
00:19:31,660 --> 00:19:32,260
Tell me,

468
00:19:33,220 --> 00:19:34,660
is it true about him and Dai Shan?

469
00:19:35,260 --> 00:19:36,377
Find it hard to believe?

470
00:19:36,977 --> 00:19:37,780
You'd rather believe

471
00:19:37,780 --> 00:19:39,140
he's with Mimi or Jia Jia?

472
00:19:43,980 --> 00:19:44,900
Dai Shan

473
00:19:45,180 --> 00:19:46,820
is Mr. Fan's ex-wife.

474
00:19:47,220 --> 00:19:47,900
So what?

475
00:19:51,100 --> 00:19:52,740
Can you take your calls outside?

476
00:19:53,266 --> 00:19:53,940
Taking it here

477
00:19:53,940 --> 00:19:55,340
disturbs everyone else.

478
00:19:55,540 --> 00:19:56,780
You think you're the sun?

479
00:19:56,933 --> 00:19:58,250
That we all revolve around you?

480
00:19:58,250 --> 00:19:59,370
You only care about dating.

481
00:19:59,370 --> 00:20:01,010
Does dating make us money?

482
00:20:01,010 --> 00:20:02,020
What are you waiting for?

483
00:20:02,020 --> 00:20:02,860
Hurry up and fix it.

484
00:20:02,940 --> 00:20:03,820
Send out a notice.

485
00:20:04,300 --> 00:20:06,580
Editors and authors cannot date.

486
00:20:06,860 --> 00:20:07,820
Otherwise, how can they

487
00:20:07,820 --> 00:20:08,620
stay objective?

488
00:20:09,177 --> 00:20:09,977
Understood, Mr. Fan.

489
00:20:10,300 --> 00:20:12,700
I hate people
who can't separate work and life.

490
00:20:16,500 --> 00:20:17,500
What is it, Fan?

491
00:20:17,980 --> 00:20:19,860
Are you serious about He Han?

492
00:20:20,540 --> 00:20:22,540
He is my top author.

493
00:20:23,020 --> 00:20:24,300
Even so, I don't want him

494
00:20:24,300 --> 00:20:25,900
to live in my apartment.

495
00:20:27,340 --> 00:20:27,980
I hope

496
00:20:28,100 --> 00:20:29,900
you remember your promise to me.

497
00:20:30,980 --> 00:20:31,940
Fine. Don't worry.

498
00:20:32,660 --> 00:20:33,820
I won't let him come over.

499
00:20:35,420 --> 00:20:37,220
"Shattered Six States" is relaunching.

500
00:20:37,860 --> 00:20:40,060
You promised me prime promotion spots.

501
00:20:40,180 --> 00:20:41,740
You'd better remember your promise, too.

502
00:20:42,540 --> 00:20:43,460
I'm driving. Bye.

503
00:20:50,340 --> 00:20:51,780
I think this judge is great.

504
00:20:52,540 --> 00:20:53,620
Is it true, Ms. Lin?

505
00:20:54,260 --> 00:20:55,860
How would I know if it's true?

506
00:20:56,460 --> 00:20:57,500
Go ask He Han yourself.

507
00:20:57,660 --> 00:20:58,660
You have his number.

508
00:20:58,820 --> 00:20:59,820
I meant Guazhou.

509
00:21:01,260 --> 00:21:03,500
Are we really writing them into Guazhou?

510
00:21:07,580 --> 00:21:08,860
Isn't it drafted and uploaded?

511
00:21:09,280 --> 00:21:11,200
On Monday,
"Drunk Old Friend" enters Guazhou.

512
00:21:11,210 --> 00:21:12,910
He Han's
"Shattered Six States" relaunches.

513
00:21:12,977 --> 00:21:14,660
If we make such huge plot changes now,

514
00:21:14,820 --> 00:21:15,940
we could lose readers.

515
00:21:20,180 --> 00:21:20,860
I'm confident.

516
00:21:21,500 --> 00:21:22,380
Once it's published,

517
00:21:22,380 --> 00:21:23,400
there's no turning back.

518
00:21:23,488 --> 00:21:24,380
If the readers hate it,

519
00:21:24,380 --> 00:21:25,220
we're done for.

520
00:21:26,700 --> 00:21:27,900
I sent it to the website.

521
00:21:28,220 --> 00:21:28,900
Stop asking.

522
00:21:29,311 --> 00:21:31,140
Prepare the next batch
of lore for He Han.

523
00:21:35,820 --> 00:21:36,380
For Gu Yan.

524
00:21:44,500 --> 00:21:47,340
(He Han)

525
00:21:57,060 --> 00:21:57,460
Hello?

526
00:21:59,020 --> 00:22:00,620
Flattering yourself, aren't you?

527
00:22:01,660 --> 00:22:03,500
Regret blowing up at me earlier,

528
00:22:03,500 --> 00:22:04,100
don't you?

529
00:22:04,980 --> 00:22:05,660
I'm sorry.

530
00:22:07,620 --> 00:22:08,660
I misunderstood you.

531
00:22:09,180 --> 00:22:09,860
It's fine.

532
00:22:10,140 --> 00:22:11,260
I'll be the bigger person.

533
00:22:11,500 --> 00:22:13,020
It's all water under the bridge.

534
00:22:13,980 --> 00:22:15,260
But I'm calling to ask,

535
00:22:16,020 --> 00:22:16,980
how is Zhangzhu?

536
00:22:17,380 --> 00:22:19,220
Did her dad
really stop her from working?

537
00:22:19,940 --> 00:22:21,660
If so, I need to talk to him.

538
00:22:22,020 --> 00:22:23,220
She's my number one fan.

539
00:22:23,220 --> 00:22:24,220
I'm responsible for her.

540
00:22:24,380 --> 00:22:25,444
I haven't contacted her.

541
00:22:26,180 --> 00:22:27,300
Even if something happened,

542
00:22:27,300 --> 00:22:28,620
it's not your place to see him.

543
00:22:29,300 --> 00:22:30,780
I'm her boss. I'll handle it.

544
00:22:31,020 --> 00:22:32,340
Fine, you handle it.

545
00:22:32,420 --> 00:22:33,780
If you can't, come to me.

546
00:22:35,660 --> 00:22:37,220
By the way, I'll drop by tomorrow.

547
00:22:37,780 --> 00:22:38,300
See you.

548
00:22:53,930 --> 00:22:57,511
♪I watch stars in my eyes♪

549
00:22:57,511 --> 00:23:00,644
♪Slowly tripped away♪

550
00:23:02,044 --> 00:23:05,109
♪I don't know it inside last night♪

551
00:23:05,110 --> 00:23:08,555
♪Cause I never see you again♪

552
00:23:09,688 --> 00:23:13,459
♪I'm waking up
to silence in the morning♪

553
00:23:13,460 --> 00:23:17,222
♪Heal, can I heal?♪

554
00:23:17,933 --> 00:23:21,239
♪All I want is nothing but♪

555
00:23:21,240 --> 00:23:24,488
♪Better see your face someday♪

556
00:23:25,133 --> 00:23:29,259
♪All I wish that you
could hear my voice♪

557
00:23:29,260 --> 00:23:34,155
♪And know that I won't forget you♪

558
00:23:34,622 --> 00:23:37,355
♪Never forget you♪

559
00:24:02,020 --> 00:24:02,700
What is this?

560
00:24:04,860 --> 00:24:05,620
About today...

561
00:24:06,220 --> 00:24:06,860
I'm sorry.

562
00:24:07,580 --> 00:24:08,660
I told San Mei

563
00:24:08,660 --> 00:24:09,580
not to come anymore.

564
00:24:10,140 --> 00:24:11,460
From now on, that's my workspace.

565
00:24:11,780 --> 00:24:12,980
You can check on me anytime.

566
00:24:13,940 --> 00:24:15,980
I shouldn't make you feel uncomfortable.

567
00:24:18,940 --> 00:24:20,180
Put this back and keep it safe.

568
00:24:20,700 --> 00:24:21,780
Who locks their girlfriend

569
00:24:21,780 --> 00:24:22,820
out of a room?

570
00:24:24,900 --> 00:24:26,420
You weren't replying to my messages.

571
00:24:27,060 --> 00:24:28,260
I thought you were mad.

572
00:24:30,140 --> 00:24:31,660
I was in a meeting with Zhiyuan.

573
00:24:32,060 --> 00:24:32,380
Right.

574
00:24:33,580 --> 00:24:34,580
I have good news.

575
00:24:35,620 --> 00:24:37,300
Zhiyuan agreed to invest.

576
00:24:38,860 --> 00:24:39,940
But I was also mad.

577
00:24:40,820 --> 00:24:41,860
Not because

578
00:24:41,860 --> 00:24:43,300
San Mei was in your room.

579
00:24:43,620 --> 00:24:45,100
That's your business.

580
00:24:45,980 --> 00:24:48,060
It's because you game all night.

581
00:24:48,380 --> 00:24:49,340
You write all day,

582
00:24:49,420 --> 00:24:50,580
