603
00:26:01,100 --> 00:26:02,220
Stop playing dumb.

604
00:26:04,780 --> 00:26:09,500
(Esports Internet Cafe, Arcades)

605
00:26:09,500 --> 00:26:10,177
Let me tell you,

606
00:26:10,300 --> 00:26:11,780
