607
00:26:12,022 --> 00:26:13,420
would Lin Zhanqiao ever go for him?

608
00:26:14,020 --> 00:26:15,500
He's a top author now.

609
00:26:15,980 --> 00:26:17,020
So what?

610
00:26:17,940 --> 00:26:19,380
Lin Zhanqiao just uses him for money.

611
00:26:19,620 --> 00:26:20,540
She'd use anyone.

612
00:26:20,955 --> 00:26:21,820
When it's all over,

613
00:26:22,100 --> 00:26:23,820
