a lousy admin here again?

614
00:26:24,820 --> 00:26:25,780
He gets it.

615
00:26:31,780 --> 00:26:32,700
We're at the bottom.

616
00:26:33,420 --> 00:26:34,340
They're at the top.

617
00:26:35,020 --> 00:26:36,020
Two different worlds.

618
00:26:36,622 --> 00:26:37,620
He goes up for a spin,

619
00:26:37,666 --> 00:26:39,900
