and comes back to brag to us.

620
00:26:39,900 --> 00:26:40,460
That's enough.

621
00:26:41,380 --> 00:26:42,260
Back to reality.

622
00:26:43,220 --> 00:26:44,860
If he really wants to be their equal,

623
00:26:45,088 --> 00:26:46,820
