good karma in this life,

624
00:26:47,220 --> 00:26:48,688
and hope for a better next life.

625
00:26:51,420 --> 00:26:52,570
He might not think that way.

626
00:26:52,570 --> 00:26:54,140
Slap him twice and he will.

627
00:26:54,860 --> 00:26:56,300
Boss, instant noodles with sausage.

628
00:26:56,980 --> 00:26:57,340
Coming.

629
00:26:57,660 --> 00:26:58,180
It's PC 16.

630
00:27:05,500 --> 00:27:06,020
Ms. Zhou.

631
00:27:06,500 --> 00:27:07,000
Why don't we

632
