640
00:27:19,740 --> 00:27:20,420
- Alright, bye.
- Bye.

641
00:27:20,420 --> 00:27:21,260
- Bye.
- See you.

642
00:27:21,340 --> 00:27:21,660
Bye.

643
00:27:32,220 --> 00:27:32,780
Ms. Zhou.

644
