651
00:27:48,460 --> 00:27:48,860
Okay.

652
00:27:49,260 --> 00:27:50,100
Thank you, Mr. Bei.

653
00:28:31,340 --> 00:28:32,266
To Three on the Bund.

654
00:28:32,340 --> 00:28:32,660
Okay.

655
00:28:37,940 --> 00:28:39,140
You lucked out today.

656
00:28:42,577 --> 00:28:43,380
