657
00:28:43,860 --> 00:28:44,980
It's an 18-year Dalmore.

658
00:28:44,980 --> 00:28:45,380
18 years?

659
00:28:46,900 --> 00:28:47,300
No wonder.

660
00:28:47,300 --> 00:28:48,266
No wonder it's strong.

661
00:28:48,444 --> 00:28:49,600
