688
00:29:33,244 --> 00:29:34,155
Can you do that?

689
00:29:35,140 --> 00:29:35,620
Can you?

690
00:29:39,155 --> 00:29:40,180
I'm not playing around.

691
00:29:40,180 --> 00:29:41,100
You said

692
00:29:41,666 --> 00:29:42,780
