701
00:29:55,088 --> 00:29:55,733
Seven million.

702
00:29:57,377 --> 00:29:58,333
I'll get it for you.

703
00:29:58,444 --> 00:29:59,377
In one month?

704
00:30:05,340 --> 00:30:05,660
Here.

705
00:30:08,140 --> 00:30:08,460
