706
00:30:09,288 --> 00:30:10,111
Take a photo.

707
00:30:12,777 --> 00:30:13,740
For our seven million.

708
00:30:14,100 --> 00:30:14,540
Come.

709
00:30:21,260 --> 00:30:24,660
(Zhao Lanxin: Party on the Bund)

710
00:30:42,740 --> 00:30:45,380
(Zhiyuan Venture Capital Allocation,
Chenxing Culture Media Co., Ltd.)

711
00:30:47,420 --> 00:30:47,900
Hello?

712
