727
00:31:18,180 --> 00:31:19,460
Removing it now.

728
00:31:20,700 --> 00:31:21,511
And your hair?

729
00:31:23,180 --> 00:31:24,820
I'll straighten it tomorrow morning.

730
00:31:25,420 --> 00:31:26,100
Don't worry.

731
00:31:26,660 --> 00:31:28,220
Shoes, bags, and clothes...

732
00:31:28,220 --> 00:31:29,060
It's all prepared.

733
00:31:29,260 --> 00:31:30,220
Armed to the teeth.

734
00:31:31,900 --> 00:31:33,300
Wish your dad a happy birthday.

735
00:31:34,260 --> 00:31:35,820
Tell him to slice the ginseng for tea.

736
00:31:37,660 --> 00:31:38,780
I'll thank you on his behalf.

737
00:31:40,100 --> 00:31:40,666
By the way,

738
00:31:40,900 --> 00:31:42,100
I have good news.

739
00:31:43,300 --> 00:31:44,410
Looks like I'll secure

740
00:31:44,410 --> 00:31:45,580
Zhiyuan's investment.

741
00:31:46,700 --> 00:31:48,820
This finally solves
my immediate problem.

742
00:31:50,180 --> 00:31:51,060
I acted so confidently

743
00:31:51,060 --> 00:31:52,780
