744
00:31:53,340 --> 00:31:55,020
But deep down, I knew

745
00:31:55,180 --> 00:31:56,660
I was almost completely broke.

746
00:31:58,340 --> 00:31:58,940
Thank you.

747
00:32:00,100 --> 00:32:00,500
Alright.

748
00:32:00,900 --> 00:32:02,300
