766
00:33:11,220 --> 00:33:12,740
So I can never let her know

767
00:33:13,020 --> 00:33:14,460
I wear heels and lipstick,

768
00:33:14,820 --> 00:33:15,860
and floral dresses.

769
00:33:17,700 --> 00:33:18,820
But your style...

770
00:33:20,140 --> 00:33:21,860
I mean your actual style.

771
00:33:22,220 --> 00:33:23,100
Does your mom know?

772
00:33:23,300 --> 00:33:23,820
No.

773
00:33:26,140 --> 00:33:28,660
She never let me wear skirts
or leather shoes when I was young.

774
00:33:29,940 --> 00:33:30,980
So when I grew up,

775
00:33:31,500 --> 00:33:32,460
all my money

776
00:33:32,980 --> 00:33:34,620
