783
00:34:11,060 --> 00:34:12,100
Here. Thanks.

784
00:34:21,860 --> 00:34:22,620
Slippers are here.

785
00:34:33,940 --> 00:34:34,420
Thanks.

786
00:34:35,460 --> 00:34:35,860
Thank you.

787
00:34:40,020 --> 00:34:40,820
