804
00:35:12,820 --> 00:35:14,860
and he wants to move back temporarily,

805
00:35:15,660 --> 00:35:16,980
I'm open to it.

806
00:35:17,100 --> 00:35:17,620
Mom.

807
00:35:18,980 --> 00:35:20,100
He's not coming back.

808
00:35:21,860 --> 00:35:22,580
Mr. Bei,

809
00:35:23,140 --> 00:35:24,180
you can tell

810
00:35:24,460 --> 00:35:25,380
my daughter and I

811
00:35:25,780 --> 00:35:26,700
are decent people.

812
00:35:29,460 --> 00:35:30,180
She's never

813
00:35:30,460 --> 00:35:31,820
even dated.

814
00:35:33,180 --> 00:35:35,140
How could we possibly

815
00:35:35,580 --> 00:35:37,700
meet with that woman?

816
00:35:38,140 --> 00:35:39,580
I don't want her

817
00:35:39,940 --> 00:35:41,940
to pollute my daughter's mind.

818
00:35:43,380 --> 00:35:44,980
Please meet her

819
00:35:45,340 --> 00:35:46,380
on our behalf.

820
00:35:47,140 --> 00:35:48,260
Tell her

821
00:35:48,700 --> 00:35:49,820
that ruining a marriage

822
00:35:50,380 --> 00:35:51,380
