823
00:35:51,660 --> 00:35:53,060
are highly immoral.

824
00:35:53,377 --> 00:35:54,900
There will be serious consequences.

825
00:35:55,220 --> 00:35:55,620
Right?

826
00:36:08,380 --> 00:36:09,100
Mr. Zhang,

827
00:36:09,940 --> 00:36:11,260
staring at my daughter like that

828
00:36:11,940 --> 00:36:13,380
seems a bit rude.

829
00:36:19,860 --> 00:36:20,300
No.

830
00:36:20,940 --> 00:36:21,380
I'm sorry.

831
00:36:21,380 --> 00:36:23,220
I just thought of some related cases.

832
00:36:23,500 --> 00:36:23,820
Right.

833
00:36:30,540 --> 00:36:31,620
You're wearing nail polish.

834
00:36:36,540 --> 00:36:38,500
