843
00:36:49,900 --> 00:36:50,500
Tell me.

844
00:36:51,060 --> 00:36:52,100
I need a word with her.

845
00:36:52,820 --> 00:36:54,380
She's a bad influence on you.

846
00:36:55,380 --> 00:36:55,980
We must

847
00:36:56,420 --> 00:36:57,020
