you need to visit our firm.

869
00:37:44,820 --> 00:37:45,700
We need to talk.

870
00:37:46,060 --> 00:37:46,620
Then,

871
00:37:46,860 --> 00:37:48,340
we have to meet your father.

872
00:37:48,620 --> 00:37:50,460
Please wait outside first.

873
00:37:53,500 --> 00:37:54,340
Take off your shoes.

874
00:37:55,460 --> 00:37:56,140
You do it,

875
00:37:56,660 --> 00:37:57,540
or I'll do it for you.

876
00:38:15,500 --> 00:38:18,420
(Changchun Apartments)

877
00:38:33,200 --> 00:38:34,300
I could get you the shoes.

878
00:38:34,580 --> 00:38:35,060
Forget it.

879
00:38:35,266 --> 00:38:35,940
Where's Mr. Bei?

880
00:38:36,380 --> 00:38:36,980
In the car.

881
00:38:37,820 --> 00:38:38,260
Careful.

882
00:38:57,780 --> 00:38:58,300
Sorry.

883
00:38:59,260 --> 00:39:00,980
You shouldn't have seen that.

884
00:39:03,180 --> 00:39:03,980
I'm a lawyer.

885
00:39:04,780 --> 00:39:05,730
Believe me,

886
00:39:05,730 --> 00:39:07,420
I've seen all kinds of clients.

887
00:39:07,755 --> 00:39:08,860
No, I just never thought

888
00:39:08,860 --> 00:39:10,660
this would happen to you.

889
00:39:13,260 --> 00:39:14,340
Shows you're still young.

890
00:39:15,580 --> 00:39:17,060
You have a lot to learn from Mr. Bei.

891
00:39:22,780 --> 00:39:23,620
Let's get you home.

892
00:39:26,100 --> 00:39:26,380
Okay.

893
00:39:32,780 --> 00:39:33,860
Growing up like that,

894
00:39:35,380 --> 00:39:37,580
and still becoming
the Zhou Mei we know,

895
00:39:38,780 --> 00:39:39,620
is truly remarkable.

896
00:39:55,020 --> 00:39:56,380
My mom was a top student.

897
00:39:58,260 --> 00:39:58,860
A prodigy.

898
00:39:59,700 --> 00:40:01,020
An apple of everyone's eyes.

899
00:40:03,020 --> 00:40:04,180
When my dad married her,

900
00:40:04,700 --> 00:40:06,660
he said he loved her brilliant mind.

901
00:40:07,540 --> 00:40:08,580
But when they divorced,

902
00:40:09,460 --> 00:40:10,940
he said she was boring.

903
00:40:12,780 --> 00:40:13,580
So your dad

904
00:40:13,820 --> 00:40:14,860
found a new wife.

905
00:40:15,140 --> 00:40:15,860
A mistress.

906
00:40:16,260 --> 00:40:17,100
Not a new wife.

907
00:40:21,940 --> 00:40:23,580
My mom knew where she lived.

908
00:40:25,420 --> 00:40:26,533
She took me there with her.

909
00:40:27,380 --> 00:40:30,340
(Year 2004)

910
00:40:40,844 --> 00:40:42,088
She acted just like

911
00:40:42,180 --> 00:40:43,540
what you saw earlier.

912
00:40:46,940 --> 00:40:47,420
And...

913
00:40:48,060 --> 00:40:48,660
What about you?

914
00:40:49,180 --> 00:40:49,660
Me?

915
00:40:58,600 --> 00:40:59,660
You wouldn't believe it.

916
00:41:01,940 --> 00:41:02,711
I was mesmerized.

917
00:41:04,220 --> 00:41:05,260
Every inch of her house

918
00:41:05,940 --> 00:41:06,980
was beautiful.

919
00:41:09,780 --> 00:41:10,700
Of course, I hated her.

920
00:41:12,460 --> 00:41:13,380
She stole my dad.

921
00:41:14,380 --> 00:41:16,420
She caused us
so much pain and humiliation.

922
00:41:19,180 --> 00:41:20,060
But at the same time,

923
00:41:21,660 --> 00:41:23,180
I really loved her clothes.

924
00:41:23,980 --> 00:41:24,780
Her jewelry.

925
00:41:26,860 --> 00:41:27,580
Even

926
00:41:28,300 --> 00:41:29,460
the smell of her house.

927
00:41:49,340 --> 00:41:52,300
♪My heart is beating still♪

928
00:41:53,420 --> 00:41:56,340
♪Sometimes I feel alone♪

929
00:41:57,100 --> 00:42:00,180
♪But love should not be frail♪

930
00:42:04,740 --> 00:42:08,060
♪Is there a spell♪

931
00:42:08,500 --> 00:42:11,540
♪that lies inside my head♪

932
00:42:11,980 --> 00:42:15,660
♪Stand naked and haunted♪

933
00:42:18,340 --> 00:42:19,940
♪If there's a way♪

934
00:42:19,940 --> 00:42:24,900
♪To save me from the blue days♪

935
00:42:25,900 --> 00:42:26,660
♪I guess♪

936
00:42:26,660 --> 00:42:31,900
♪It's rising from my silence♪

937
00:42:33,500 --> 00:42:35,980
♪I'm nothing but the one♪

938
00:42:35,980 --> 00:42:40,100
♪Who paints the blue sky♪

939
00:42:41,180 --> 00:42:42,780
♪With all of my tears♪

940
00:42:42,780 --> 00:42:44,460
♪And past pain♪

941
00:42:44,740 --> 00:42:46,700
♪I'd still try♪

942
00:42:49,940 --> 00:42:53,420
♪Please stay with me♪

943
00:42:54,020 --> 00:42:57,460
♪I could've held you in my arms♪

944
00:42:58,020 --> 00:43:00,260
♪When I said love♪

945
00:43:00,260 --> 00:43:03,260
♪Hurts somehow♪

946
00:43:05,921 --> 00:43:07,041
(I've been thinking.)

947
00:43:08,321 --> 00:43:11,601
(Everyone's most comfortable level of intimacy)

948
00:43:12,361 --> 00:43:19,691
(is probably different.)

949
00:43:20,691 --> 00:43:22,441
♪If the sky♪

950
00:43:22,951 --> 00:43:24,351
♪And the sea♪

951
00:43:24,891 --> 00:43:26,601
♪Turned upside down♪

952
00:43:28,161 --> 00:43:30,091
♪If a swimming fish♪

953
00:43:30,491 --> 00:43:33,881
♪Fell in love with a flying bird♪

954
00:43:35,651 --> 00:43:37,621
♪If back then♪

955
00:43:37,981 --> 00:43:42,391
♪We had never let go♪

956
00:43:42,991 --> 00:43:49,271
♪We wouldn't be lost in the crowd♪

957
00:43:50,391 --> 00:43:52,541
♪We met in a thirteenth month♪

958
00:43:52,541 --> 00:43:54,411
♪Held each other in a fifth season♪

959
00:43:54,591 --> 00:43:57,031
♪And found our way back whole♪

960
00:43:57,871 --> 00:44:00,041
♪So let this surging love♪

961
00:44:00,041 --> 00:44:04,471
♪Rise like tides that never fall♪

962
00:44:05,371 --> 00:44:07,551
♪If we're caught in a pouring rain♪

963
00:44:07,551 --> 00:44:08,641
♪That's alright♪

964
00:44:09,181 --> 00:44:09,931
♪If we're buried♪

965
00:44:09,931 --> 00:44:12,631
♪By passing years all the better♪

966
00:44:12,891 --> 00:44:15,071
♪At least we still can keep♪

967
00:44:15,251 --> 00:44:19,671
♪This one eternal photograph♪

968
00:44:35,431 --> 00:44:37,721
♪We're on misaligned tracks♪

969
00:44:37,721 --> 00:44:39,481
♪Running in opposite ways♪

970
00:44:39,601 --> 00:44:42,071
♪Searching all along the way♪

971
00:44:42,871 --> 00:44:45,031
♪For the fire of our younger hearts♪

972
00:44:45,221 --> 00:44:50,131
♪And the beauty lost in time♪

973
00:44:50,131 --> 00:44:53,651
♪This time don't lose each other again♪

974
00:44:53,891 --> 00:44:54,861
♪Only after loss♪

975
00:44:54,861 --> 00:44:57,491
♪Do we learn what truly matters most♪

976
00:44:57,901 --> 00:45:00,261
♪In another time and space♪

977
00:45:00,261 --> 00:45:01,821
♪We'll stay and walk together♪

978
00:45:01,821 --> 00:45:04,651
♪Till we grow old♪

979
00:45:05,611 --> 00:45:07,901
♪But still the sky will never♪

980
00:45:07,901 --> 00:45:10,571
♪Turn with the sea♪

981
00:45:13,091 --> 00:45:15,501
♪But still a swimming fish won't♪

982
00:45:15,501 --> 00:45:20,711
♪Fall in love with a flying bird♪
